Classes should be concatenated

```
word{.a #a class=b #b .c}
.
<p><span class="a b c" id="b">word</span></p>
```

Automatic and explicit classes should be merged correctly

```
{.a}
::: b
:::
.
<div class="a b">
</div>
```

classes, identifiers and keys can contain ':', '_', '-' and alphanumeric
characters.

```
a{.-}
a{.0}
a{.:}
a{._}
a{.a}
.
<p><span class="-">a</span>
<span class="0">a</span>
<span class=":">a</span>
<span class="_">a</span>
<span class="a">a</span></p>
```

```
a{#-}
a{#0}
a{#:}
a{#_}
a{#a}
.
<p><span id="-">a</span>
<span id="0">a</span>
<span id=":">a</span>
<span id="_">a</span>
<span id="a">a</span></p>
```

