Keys must be followed by '='

```
a{a=a}
a{a.a}
a{a#a}
.
<p><span a="a">a</span>
a{a.a}
a{a#a}</p>
```

Values cannot start with other symbols unless quoted

```
a{a=aa}
a{a=:a}
a{a=?a}
a{a="?a"}
.
<p><span a="aa">a</span>
<span a=":a">a</span>
a{a=?a}
<span a="?a">a</span></p>
```
